


additional dependencies 
AsyncStorage for data persistence(`npm install @react-native-async-storage/async-storage`
)
React Navigation for navigation (`npm install @react-navigation/native @react-navigation/stack`
)
Styled Components for styling (`npm install styled-components @types/styled-components --legacy-peer-deps`
) <br>
used  `--legacy-peer-deps` to bypass the warnings in npm install


React Native Vector Icons for icons
React Native Elements for UI Kit
React Native Picker Select for date picker
React Native Picker for time picker
React Native Date Picker for date picker
React Native Swipe Gesture Handler for swipe gesture


app structure
Screens:
TasksList: Displays all tasks
AddTask: to add new task
EditTask: Form to edit the details of an existing task

Components:
TaskItem: Displays individual tasks.
TaskForm: A reusable form component for creating/editing tasks.

State Management:
Use useState and useEffect hooks for managing task data.
Use AsyncStorage for persisting tasks.